message.body: Hey what are you doing tomorrow
I'm having a tiny and casual grad party that's pretty much a few members of my family + Sam and there'll be sandwiches and black forest cake and stuff and f you're around you should stop by :)
It starts around 6, dessert's around 7, and we're going to go up and watch the swarthmore college graduates' fireworks display at 9, so whenever you like/whatever you wanna show up for really :)
